title: Secret Beyond the Door... (1947 Film-Noir) by Fritz Lang - where love meets fear

sources.title: Secret Beyond the Door... (1947 Film-Noir) by Fritz Lang - where love meets fear
sources.description:
Celia Lamphere marries the enigmatic Mark, only to discover his mansion hides a locked room and a chilling obsession with recreating infamous crime scenes, and she discovers that he may want to kill her?

Original title: Secret Beyond the Door...

Director: Fritz Lang
Writers: Silvia Richards, Rufus King

Main cast:
Joan Bennett - Celia Lamphere
Michael Redgrave - Mark Lamphere
Anne Revere - Caroline Lamphere
Barbara O'Neil - Miss Robey

Genres: Drama, Film-Noir, Mystery, Romance, Thriller
Release date: December 24, 1947
Filming location: USA
